00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:38,360
of a fountain taken this afternoon, we feed it millions of random historical

1642
00:44:38,560 --> 00:44:41,160
tourist photos of a city center from the 1980s.

1643
00:44:41,360 --> 00:44:44,480
Oh, wow. Millions of physical photos pulled from attics,

